{"tid":1188561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持都會票領交通補貼  竟被大叔搶先拍卡  乘客斥如同搶錢","createTime":"2019-06-06T10:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:54:56.000Z","uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4a04926ee98840e180f0db3edda97933be7566","tid":1188561,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190606/_2019060610180763882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190606%2F_2019060610180763882.jpg&h=117b49a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「公共交通費用補貼計畫」自今年1月1日起實施後，首四個月分別約有235萬、194萬、236萬和218萬名市民受惠。有網民稱昨日拍卡領取補貼時，被一名大叔從後搶先拍卡，「搶走」補貼，呼籲乘客小心。<br />\n<br />\n網民Raymond Leung在Facebook群組「將軍澳」發文，指昨晚在一個港鐵站登記都會票領取交通補貼時，被人從後搶先拍卡「搶補貼」，「當我拍完都會票，正準備拍八達通，突然一個地中海，頭髮留長，年齡大概五六十嘅阿叔，竟然二話不說，衝上嚟用佢張八達通鎖匙扣拍咗落去，比佢搶咗個登記！」<br />\n<br />\n網民指，大叔聲稱以為部機係領津貼，故拍了卡，「但好人好者，明明有人用緊部機，又點會搶住拍佢個八達通。此人非常可疑，各位小心。」他當時向港鐵職員求助，但對方未能處理，建議再重新登記。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起其他網民討論，「同搶錢有咩分别呀，即時叫港鐵職員處理啦」、「真是搶錢」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31eVuSX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31eVuSX&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=3e9ba013\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31eVuSX</a>"},{"pid":"9f84b273dd6186560278a64d089727d9a0ae8c75","tid":1188561,"uid":6222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"之後點又唔講<br />\n<br />\n放生佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c869122a4ed4411240b97c1c69c45387a60f214","tid":1188561,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f84b273dd6186560278a64d089727d9a0ae8c75","tid":1188561,"uid":6222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"之後點又唔講<br />\n<br />\n放生佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"即場報警啦"},{"pid":"d3d97020e702b866ab95dc1dec755b310825b641","tid":1188561,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c869122a4ed4411240b97c1c69c45387a60f214","tid":1188561,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f84b273dd6186560278a64d089727d9a0ae8c75","tid":1188561,"uid":6222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"之後點又唔講<br />\n<br />\n放生佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"即場報警啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係癈佬藍絲 點會處理<br />\n<br />\n沒事兒"},{"pid":"2f835631aee4430076f40774a926d597b45538d1","tid":1188561,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"問佢攞返錢咪得，好小事"},{"pid":"9bc50ef84be43776754465e561cb969743680f6c","tid":1188561,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"警又唔報，講條春咩"},{"pid":"74678203d3b8c18589ab587c11bd7228e2465a23","tid":1188561,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bc50ef84be43776754465e561cb969743680f6c","tid":1188561,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"警又唔報，講條春咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}